lead_paragraph: The Colorado Rockies have had some of the uncertainty surrounding Jose Reyes' status resolved, at least for spring training, but manager Walt Weiss says he understands the process is still unfolding.

headline.print_headline: Rockies Adjust to Spring Training Without Jose Reyes
